ciation": "OWNER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "\r\n[New from Anaconda: Python in the Browser](https://www.anaconda.com/blog/pyscript-python-in-the-browser)\r\n\r\n## Pyodide\u3092CDN\u7d4c\u7531\u3067\u30a4\u30f3\u30dd\u30fc\u30c8\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<head>\r\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/pyodide/v0.20.0/full/pyodide.js\"></script>\r\n</head>\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Python\u30b9\u30af\u30ea\u30d7\u30c8\u306e\u5b9f\u884c\r\n\r\n`const pyodide = await loadPyodide();` \u3067\u521d\u671f\u5316\u51e6\u7406\u3092\u884c\u306a\u3063\u3066\u304a\u308a\u3001`pyodide.runPython` \u3067\u30b9\u30af\u30ea\u30d7\u30c8\u306e\u5b9f\u884c\u3092\u884c\u3046\u3002\r\n\r\n\u30d1\u30c3\u30b1\u30fc\u30b8\u306e\u30a4\u30f3\u30dd\u30fc\u30c8\u306b\u95a2\u3057\u3066\u306f\u52d5\u4f5c\u78ba\u8a8d\u4e2d\r\n\r\n- \u30d5\u30a1\u30a4\u30eb\u69cb\u6210\r\n\r\n```\r\n- index.html\r\n- scripts/\r\n  - get_version.py\r\n  - get_zen.py \r\n```\r\n\r\n- `index.html`\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<h2>Python: <span id=\"python-version\"></span></h2>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div id=\"python-zen\"></div>\r\n\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\r\nasync function setScriptValue(pyodide, dir, tag) {\r\n  const script = await (await fetch(dir)).text()\r\n  document.getElementById(tag).innerText = pyodide.runPython(script)\r\n}\r\nasync function main(){\r\n    const pyodide = await loadPyodide();\r\n    setScriptValue(pyodide, \"scripts/get_zen.py\", \"python-zen\")\r\n    setScriptValue(pyodide, \"scripts/get_version.py\", \"python-version\")\r\n}\r\nmain();\r\n</script>\r\n```\r\n\r\n- `scripts/get_zen.py`\r\n\r\n```python\r\nimport io\r\nfrom contextlib import redirect_stdout\r\n\r\nstdout = io.StringIO()\r\n\r\nwith redirect_stdout(stdout):\r\n    import this\r\n\r\nstdout.getvalue()\r\n```\r\n\r\n- `scripts/get_version.py`\r\n\r\n```python\r\nimport sys\r\n\r\nf\"{sys.version_info.major}.{sys.version_info.minor}.{sys.version_info.micro}\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n## ...(TBD)\r\n\r\n\u4eca\u5f8c\u78ba\u8a8d\u6b21\u7b2c\u8ffd\u8a18\u3057\u307e\u3059\u3002\r\n\r\n## \u30b3\u30fc\u30c9\u3068\u30c6\u30b9\u30c8\u30da\u30fc\u30b8\r\n\r\n\u4eca\u56de\u5229\u7528\u3057\u305f\u30b3\u30fc\u30c9\u306f[\u3053\u3061\u3089](https://github.com/kemu3007/pyodide-sample)\u3001\u4f5c\u6210\u3057\u305f\u30da\u30fc\u30b8\u306f[\u3053\u3061\u3089](https://kemu3007.github.io/pyodide-sample/)\u304b\u3089\u78ba\u8a8d\u3059\u308b\u3053\u3068\u304c\u3067\u304d\u307e\u3059\u3002", "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/40/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/kemu3007/portal/issues/40/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null}